    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it says there's a risk but i've read a lot of stuff online saying that since it's just a natural herb it's usually fine if you don't go too crazy with the dose. my doctor is super busy and i cant really get an appointment before my exams start next week. wouldn't it be alright if i just took a small amount like once a day to get through the week?",
